45#ifdef HAVE_CONFIG_H
46#include <config.h>
47#endif
48
49#include "key.h"
50
51#define soft_limit 0x10000
52
53srtp_err_status_t srtp_key_limit_set(srtp_key_limit_t key,
54 const srtp_xtd_seq_num_t s)
55{
56#ifdef NO_64BIT_MATH
57 if (high32(s) == 0 && low32(s) < soft_limit) {
58 return srtp_err_status_bad_param;
59 }
60#else
61 if (s < soft_limit) {
62 return srtp_err_status_bad_param;
63 }
64#endif
65 key->num_left = s;
66 key->state = srtp_key_state_normal;
67 return srtp_err_status_ok;
68}
69
70srtp_err_status_t srtp_key_limit_clone(srtp_key_limit_t original,
71 srtp_key_limit_t *new_key)
72{
73 if (original == NULL) {
74 return srtp_err_status_bad_param;
75 }
76 *new_key = original;
77 return srtp_err_status_ok;
78}
79
80srtp_err_status_t srtp_key_limit_check(const srtp_key_limit_t key)
81{
82 if (key->state == srtp_key_state_expired) {
83 return srtp_err_status_key_expired;
84 }
85 return srtp_err_status_ok;
86}
87
88srtp_key_event_t srtp_key_limit_update(srtp_key_limit_t key)
89{
90#ifdef NO_64BIT_MATH
91 if (low32(key->num_left) == 0) {
92 // carry
93 key->num_left =
94 make64(high32(key->num_left) - 1, low32(key->num_left) - 1);
95 } else {
96 // no carry
97 key->num_left = make64(high32(key->num_left), low32(key->num_left) - 1);
98 }
99 if (high32(key->num_left) != 0 || low32(key->num_left) >= soft_limit) {
100 return srtp_key_event_normal; /* we're above the soft limit */
101 }
102#else
103 key->num_left--;
104 if (key->num_left >= soft_limit) {
105 return srtp_key_event_normal; /* we're above the soft limit */
106 }
107#endif
108 if (key->state == srtp_key_state_normal) {
109 /* we just passed the soft limit, so change the state */
110 key->state = srtp_key_state_past_soft_limit;
111 }
112#ifdef NO_64BIT_MATH
113 if (low32(key->num_left) == 0 && high32(key->num_left == 0))
114#else
115 if (key->num_left < 1)
116#endif
117 { /* we just hit the hard limit */
118 key->state = srtp_key_state_expired;
119 return srtp_key_event_hard_limit;
120 }
121 return srtp_key_event_soft_limit;
122}
